<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>New Pharmacy</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .pharmacy-details {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>New Pharmacy Registration</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Hello Admin,</h2>
    <p>A new pharmacy has been registered and is awaiting your approval.</p>

    <div class="pharmacy-details">
      <h3>Pharmacy Details:</h3>
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{pharmacyName}}</p>
      <p><strong>Owner:</strong> {{pharmacyOwner}}</p>
      <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{pharmacyLocation}}</p>
      <p><strong>Contact Email:</strong> {{contactEmail}}</p>
      <p><strong>Contact Phone:</strong> {{contactPhone}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>Please review the registration details and take appropriate action.</p>

    <a href="{{adminDashboardUrl}}" class="button">Review Registration</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
      Best regards,<br>
      Your Healthcare Platform Team
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>